article.description: — Samir Stewart had 12 points as Manhattan defeated Fairfield 69-59 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Stewart scores 12 to lead Manhattan over Fairfield 69-59
article.linkText: Stewart scores 12 to lead Manhattan over Fairfield 69-59
article.story: NEW YORK -- — Samir Stewart had 12 points as Manhattan defeated Fairfield 69-59 on Thursday night. Warren Williams had 12 points and three blocks for Manhattan (7-11, 6-11 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Ant Nelson added six rebounds. Caleb Green scored a season-high 21 points for the Stags (6-16, 6-11). ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
